01:04:40,861 --> 01:04:43,780
on the campus of Culver
University earlier today.

477
01:04:43,864 --> 01:04:47,117
Sophomores Jack McGee and Jim Wilson
witnessed some of the battle.

478
01:04:47,200 --> 01:04:48,660
JIM: It was so big.

479
01:04:48,743 --> 01:04:51,621
It was like this huge, like, hulk!
Yeah.

480
01:04:51,705 --> 01:04:54,791
FEMALE REPORTER: McGee, who happens to
be a reporter for the campus paper,

